name: KR1 Seeks Main Market Listing on London Stock Exchange Next Month
description: The stitched Goliath of finance ascends the teal-lit ziggurat. Its ceremonial hand dissolves into procedural cyan light, offering the heavy, glitching VHS tape of its previous existence. Before the AI Cathedral, legacy is traded for sacred noise and institutional gravity.
